track_notes: A circular walk from the small car park at Maggies Bridge, first to MELLBREAK LD-036, down into Mosedale. The climb to Hen Comb (LDW-171) is steep. Gavel Fell (LDW-158) is next on our way to BLAKE FELL LD-031. The last Wainwright is Burnbank Fell LDW-183.

Felldyke car park has a separate entrance from the road. Follow a foot path to get onto the road to Cogra Moss. Follow the main round the lake path then break off up to the ridge. Follow this to the summit. Allow 1 - 1.5 hours.
